Table Tag
---------
<table>
<caption> = Table Name
<thead> = table head (used to represent first row in a table generally heading)
<tbody> = table body (used to represent table content)
<tfoot> = table foot (used to represent last row in a table generally footer)
<tr> = table row
<td> = table data(represents column)
<th> = table heading (Makes content of first row of a table in bold)
<colgroup> = group columns
<col> = represents individual column

rowspan = rowspan is for converting multiple rows into single row
colspan = colspan is mainly used for converting multiple columns into single column